Your current array is of `String` type, and therefore the `Arrays.sort()` operation will sort the array lexicographically, as _text_, and not as integers.  To sort numerically, use:

&lt;!-- language: java --&gt;

    Arrays.sort(contents, Comparator.comparingInt(Integer::valueOf));

